Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.44,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:08.19,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:11.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen it once \Nsince the saucer came.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:15.08,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we could, \Nit's still half a month away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:15.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:19.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san's been waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:21.87,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Since that day seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.47,0:00:29.44,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Please everyone, \Nlet's enter the Hokubi Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:04.31,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,1)}What She Believes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.31,sora-main-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Mizusaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:06.21,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:11.08,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you seriously \Nentering the Hokubi Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:13.23,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to get \Nready to study abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:14.65,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:18.46,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,But she's kind of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:23.17,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, do you have plans later?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.13,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:27.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:34.25,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to discuss something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.68,Form,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi Festival Participation Form
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.68,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.74,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.82,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Got funding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.65,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That was too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:08.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I wrote Shione's name \Ndown as a participant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:13.13,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,The Hokubi Festival, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.58,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.01,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, the five of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.76,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you wanted to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.33,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.13,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Third years are supposed \Nto join independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.51,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.14,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're all here, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:34.05,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Togawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.02,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like this, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.07,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.45,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.84,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.10,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I think they go on your fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.57,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I got dragged out here suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.10,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.40,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I know, it must be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.44,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's your sister's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.08,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It was Komiya's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.26,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.78,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You'd know, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.38,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.56,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.18,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.29,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.01,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:43.06,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It tends to be something really \Nstupid that sets it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:47.79,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.08,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what we're making.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.85,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know what to look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:57.62,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Komiya did all this \Nresearch by herself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.40,Plans,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a planetarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.85,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,A planetarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.58,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.58,Prep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Prep Room 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.87,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,We're just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.96,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late. \NLet's start working tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.62,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.05,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.19,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, if you don't mind, see you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.46,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.17,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.72,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Shorty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.24,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, you were waiting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:05:59.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.71,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.08,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You should come if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.09,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.46,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's a special golden ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.23,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.23,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You can give it to friends and family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.86,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my chance to give her one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.74,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:38.75,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.43,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Things get bad when I'm \Nfar from the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Things get bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, did you watch the \Nmeteor shower with Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.02,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Can Shione smile with you guys, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.63,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. The fridge is full today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.45,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Really? How about a rice omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:17.56,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.62,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to draw on \Nit with the ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.34,Prep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Prep Room 3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.45,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.80,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of shoddy looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:34.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.95,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This prototype may not look like much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.98,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but it took a lot of effort \Nand spare time to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,First, the light bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:43.51,sora-overlap,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:47.48,sora-overlap,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We put a plastic sheet over this light \Nbulb. It has the Kiriyako City sky on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.41,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It should, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:56.28,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't we use that \Nthing you made, Togawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.54,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, this should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:03.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I helped, so I'm looking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.54,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuzuki, everyone else helped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.60,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.55,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If it works, let's all take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.74,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.17,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.13,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm turning on the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:28.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bright enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.70,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I think it just needs more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, that probably wouldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.57,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:39.92,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.21,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are they okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.59,0:08:45.80,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Max power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.52,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:54.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Water! Firetruck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.08,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.89,sora-overlap,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No, cut the power first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.55,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.40,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.65,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one that messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.41,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.53,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So do you always have these with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.29,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to eat \Nwith you guys today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.17,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.43,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.06,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.45,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.12,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:08.46,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Nonoka said we \Nshould call the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.34,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Remember we all got prepared, \Nlike we did today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about how we should do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.84,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,and we tried all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.86,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty stupid in retrospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.48,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.14,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,And a saucer actually came.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.86,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Did we really call that saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:10.98,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.32,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.73,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But we're in different schools, \Nso we can only meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:21.16,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki and Souta are twins, \Nbut they're really different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.30,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But they're really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.31,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu's really, really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.65,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.62,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's friends with Mom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.68,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to watch the stars together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.75,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,The stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.59,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.48,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We promised to watch \Nthe meteor shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.21,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.33,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.79,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you staying here, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:53.77,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.54,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If Shione comes, \Ncan you tell her something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.61,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to meet her, \Nbut I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.13,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:03.94,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.66,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her when I do, let's watch \Nthe meteor shower together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.33,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.42,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.05,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:25.64,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:30.47,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.97,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, does it hurt somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.92,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make it better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.10,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.94,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.44,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.79,Keep Out,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.80,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.33,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.43,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.06,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.41,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.33,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.53,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.53,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka went far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.88,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.16,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But Nonoka told me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.48,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,that she's coming back right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:41.75,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,so she wants to watch the \Nmeteor shower with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.54,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.63,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.14,Festival,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi \NFestival
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.14,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.98,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.65,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.46,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.84,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:08.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Things get bad when I'm \Nfar from the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:14.31,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get in without this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.38,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to watch the \Nmeteor shower with Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.20,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.13,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I didn't \Nexplain it to you properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:33.14,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,No, you did fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you smile together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.25,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.06,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Nonoka's a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's not a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.45,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's coming now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.36,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to watch the meteor \Nshower together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.87,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come back \Nfor after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.91,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.33,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.87,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.72,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of my trust being betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.72,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka came back, like she promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.88,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:06.85,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault for not being \Nable to trust her completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:10.00,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:11.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.72,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:18.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You all haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:24.93,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka kept her promise, so now \Nit's my turn to grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.25,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.75,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, let's watch the \Nmeteor shower together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.37,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a good view this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.26,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Let me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Now's a good time, \Nso tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.22,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like her or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.22,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I got a lot of help from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:18.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite a meteor shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't keep my promise, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:25.46,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.16,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the same as back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.80,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that, so why did I wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.12,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Togawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.02,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:50.94,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come back for, \Nafter all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:01.81,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say it's to \Nkeep my promise to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:06.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd really forgotten about \Nthis town until I met Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:08.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.83,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Even Yuzuki and Koharu and Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:15.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying not to \Nremember those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for Noel, I probably \Nwouldn't have even thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.72,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.93,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to watch a \Nmeteor shower with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling's always been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:39.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.36,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:47.66,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,You're my precious, precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.21,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.46,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:59.45,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't trust my beloved friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.34,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.50,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,And about Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.35,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch the meteor \Nshower with you this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.17,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be friends with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.08,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.78,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Togawa Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.49,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:34.71,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:56.61,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,A planetarium in place \Nof a meteor shower, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.76,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a good view this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.25,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:13.26,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.34,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shione coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said she'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:26.86,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:29.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:35.70,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.40,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:45.53,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You were the same Nonoka \Nthat I knew before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.16,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:49.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,we can't be together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.85,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial Method{\i0}: \N"The Meaning of Goodbye."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.26,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:39.77,sora-next-ep,,0000,0000,0000,,The Meaning of Goodbye
